{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28b0a4ba4ffe21O4BCcP31nHt7","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d74f5cd1f001wZVP3dc6nPWbC9","parts":[{"id":"prt_d74f5d9f70011UWvr7ebm4ZHmh","messageID":"msg_d74f5cd1f001wZVP3dc6nPWbC9","sessionID":"ses_28b0a4ba4ffe21O4BCcP31nHt7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_10ff1d43738c4fb2830b615e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/addon.xml"},"output":"<path>/workspace/addon.xml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"yes\"?>\n2: <addon id=\"plugin.video.netflix\" name=\"Netflix\" version=\"1.23.5+matrix.1\" provider-name=\"libdev, jojo, asciidisco, caphm, castagnait\">\n3:   <requires>\n4:     <import addon=\"xbmc.python\" version=\"3.0.0\"/>\n5:     <import addon=\"script.module.addon.signals\" version=\"0.0.6+matrix.1\"/>\n6:     <import addon=\"script.module.inputstreamhelper\" version=\"0.5.0+matrix.1\"/>\n7:     <import addon=\"script.module.pycryptodome\" version=\"3.4.3\"/>\n8:     <import addon=\"script.module.requests\"/>\n9:     <import addon=\"script.module.myconnpy\" version=\"8.0.18+matrix.1\"/> <!--MySQL Connector/Python-->\n10:   </requires>\n11:   <extension point=\"xbmc.python.pluginsource\" library=\"addon.py\">\n12:     <provides>video</provides>\n13:   </extension>\n14:   <extension point=\"xbmc.service\" library=\"service.py\"/>\n15:   <extension point=\"xbmc.addon.metadata\">\n16:     <reuselanguageinvoker>true</reuselanguageinvoker>\n17:     <summary lang=\"cs_CZ\">Netflix</summary>\n18:     <description lang=\"cs_CZ\">Plugin pro sledování filmů, seriálů online z Netflixu</description>\n19:     <disclaimer lang=\"cs_CZ\">Použití tohoto doplňku nemusí být ve vaší zemi pobytu legální - před instalací dbejte na vaše zákony.</disclaimer>\n20:     <summary lang=\"de_DE\">Netflix</summary>\n21:     <description lang=\"de_DE\">Addon für Netflix VOD-Dienste</description>\n22:     <disclaimer lang=\"de_DE\">Möglicherweise ist die Verwendung dieses Addons in Ihrem Land illegal, Sie sollten dies unbedingt vor der Installation überprüfen.</disclaimer>\n23:     <summary lang=\"en_GB\">Netflix</summary>\n24:     <description lang=\"en_GB\">Netflix VOD Services Add-on</description>\n25:     <disclaimer lang=\"en_GB\">The use of this add-on may not be legal in your country of residence - please check with your local laws before installing.</disclaimer>\n26:     <summary lang=\"el_GR\">Νέτφλιξ</summary>\n27:     <description lang=\"el_GR\">Πρόσθετο υπηρεσιών κατά παραγγελία του Νέτφλιξ</description>\n28:     <disclaimer lang=\"el_GR\">Η χρήση αυτού του προσθέτου μπορεί να μην είναι νόμιμη στην χώρα που κατοικείτε - παρακαλώ ελέγξτε τους τοπικούς νόμους πριν την εγκατάσταση.</disclaimer>\n29:     <summary lang=\"nl_NL\">Netflix</summary>\n30:     <description lang=\"nl_NL\">Bekijk Netflix films en tvprogramma's in Kodi.</description>\n31:     <disclaimer lang=\"nl_NL\">Sommige delen van deze add-on zijn mogelijk onwettig in jouw land - raadpleeg de lokale wetgeving alvorens deze add-on te installeren.</disclaimer>\n32:     <summary lang=\"ja_JP\">Netflix</summary>\n33:     <description lang=\"ja_JP\">Netflix VOD サービスアドオン</description>\n34:     <disclaimer lang=\"ja_JP\">一部の国では、このアドオンを使用するのが不法でありますので、設置する前に必ず関連法律を確認してください</disclaimer>\n35:     <summary lang=\"ko_KR\">Netflix</summary>\n36:     <description lang=\"ko_KR\">Netflix VOD 서비스애드온</description>\n37:     <disclaimer lang=\"ko_KR\">일부 국가에서는 이 애드온을 사용하는 것이 불법일 수도 있으니, 설치하기전 관련 법을 확인하기 바랍니다.</disclaimer>\n38:     <description lang=\"it_IT\">Netflix Add-on servizi VOD</description>\n39:     <disclaimer lang=\"it_IT\">L'utilizzo di questo add-on potrebbe non essere legale nel vostro paese di residenza - si prega di verificare le leggi in vigore prima dell'installazione.</disclaimer>\n40:     <summary lang=\"es_ES\">Netflix</summary>\n41:     <description lang=\"es_ES\">Complemento para los Servicios VOD de Netflix</description>\n42:     <disclaimer lang=\"es_ES\">El uso de este complemento puede no ser legal en su país de residencia - Por favor, consulte las leyes locales antes de instalarlo.</disclaimer>\n43:     <summary lang=\"hu_HU\">Netflix</summary>\n44:     <description lang=\"hu_HU\">Netflix VOD kiegészítő a Kodihoz</description>\n45:     <disclaimer lang=\"hu_HU\">Előfordulhat, hogy a kiegészítő használata nem törvényes az Ön országában - telepítés előtt tájékozódjon a helyi törvényekről</disclaimer>\n46:     <summary lang=\"pt_BR\">Netflix</summary>\n47:     <description lang=\"pt_BR\">Add-on para os serviços VOD do Netflix</description>\n48:     <disclaimer lang=\"pt_BR\">O uso deste addon pode não ser legal no seu país de residência - por favor, verifique as suas leis locais antes de instalar.</disclaimer>\n49:     <summary lang=\"tr_TR\">Netflix</summary>\n50:     <description lang=\"tr_TR\">Netflix VOD Hizmetleri Eklentisi</description>\n51:     <disclaimer lang=\"tr_TR\">Bu eklentinin bazı bölümleri ikamet ettiğiniz ülkede yasal olmayabilir - lütfen yüklemeden önce yerel yasalarınıza bakın.</disclaimer>\n52:     <summary lang=\"ro_RO\">Netflix</summary>\n53:     <description lang=\"ro_RO\">Add-on pentru servicii video la cerere Netflix</description>\n54:     <disclaimer lang=\"ro_RO\">Utilizarea acestui add-on ar putea fi ilegală în țara în care locuiți - vă rugăm să verificați legile locale înainte de instalare.</disclaimer>\n55:     <summary lang=\"sv_SE\">Netflix</summary>\n56:     <description lang=\"sv_SE\">Netflix VOD Service-tillägg</description>\n57:     <disclaimer lang=\"sv_SE\">Användandet av detta tillägg kanske inte är lagligt i ditt hemland - kontrollera med dina lokala lagar innan du installerar.</disclaimer>\n58:     <summary lang=\"zh_CN\">Netflix</summary>\n59:     <description lang=\"zh_CN\">Netflix VOD服务附加组件</description>\n60:     <disclaimer lang=\"zh_CN\">此附加组件在您的居住国可能不合法-请在安装前与您当地的法律核对。</disclaimer>\n61:     <summary lang=\"fr_FR\">Netflix</summary>\n62:     <description lang=\"fr_FR\">Extension Netflix SVoD</description>\n63:     <disclaimer lang=\"fr_FR\">L'utilisation de cette extension n'est peut-être pas légale dans votre pays de résidence - renseignez-vous avant de l'installer</disclaimer>\n64:     <summary lang=\"pl_PL\">Netflix</summary>\n65:     <description lang=\"pl_PL\">Wtyczka dla usług VOD serwisu Netflix</description>\n66:     <disclaimer lang=\"pl_PL\">Korzystanie z tego dodatku może być niezgodne z prawem w twoim kraju zamieszkania - przed zainstalowaniem zapoznaj się z lokalnymi przepisami.</disclaimer>\n67:     <summary lang=\"he_IL\">Netflix</summary>\n68:     <description lang=\"he_IL\">תוסף VOD לשירות של Netflix</description>\n69:     <disclaimer lang=\"he_IL\">השימוש בתוסף זה עלול להיות לא חוקי במדינת מגוריך - אנא בדוק את החוק ברשות המקומית לפני ההתקנה</disclaimer>\n70:     <summary lang=\"zh_TW\">Netflix</summary>\n71:     <description lang=\"zh_TW\">Netflix VOD服務套件</description>\n72:     <disclaimer lang=\"zh_TW\">在您居住的國家使用此套件可能並不合法 - 請在安裝前與您當地的法律核對</disclaimer>\n73: \t  <assets>\n74:       <icon>resources/media/icon.png</icon>\n75:       <fanart>resources/media/fanart.jpg</fanart>\n76:       <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-01.jpg</screenshot>\n77:       <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-02.jpg</screenshot>\n78:       <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-03.jpg</screenshot>\n79:       <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-04.jpg</screenshot>\n80:       <screenshot>resources/media/screenshot-05.jpg</screenshot>\n81:     </assets>\n82:     <language>en cs de es fr he hr hu it ja ko nl pl pt ro sv tr zh</language>\n83:     <platform>all</platform>\n84:     <license>MIT</license>\n85:     <website>https://www.netflix.com</website>\n86:     <email></email>\n87:     <forum>https://forum.kodi.tv/showthread.php?tid=329767</forum>\n88:     <source>https://github.com/CastagnaIT/plugin.video.netflix</source>\n89:     <news>v1.23.5 (2025-08-24)\n90: - Fix esn error on login due to website changes\n91: - Fix Nonetype error on startup due to website changes\n92:     </news>\n93:   </extension>\n94: </addon>\n\n(End of file - total 94 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"yes\"?>\n<addon id=\"plugin.video.netflix\" name=\"Netflix\" version=\"1.23.5+matrix.1\" provider-name=\"libdev, jojo, asciidisco, caphm, castagnait\">\n  <requires>\n    <import addon=\"xbmc.python\" version=\"3.0.0\"/>\n    <import addon=\"script.module.addon.signals\" version=\"0.0.6+matrix.1\"/>\n    <import addon=\"script.module.inputstreamhelper\" version=\"0.5.0+matrix.1\"/>\n    <import addon=\"script.module.pycryptodome\" version=\"3.4.3\"/>\n    <import addon=\"script.module.requests\"/>\n    <import addon=\"script.module.myconnpy\" version=\"8.0.18+matrix.1\"/> <!--MySQL Connector/Python-->\n  </requires>\n  <extension point=\"xbmc.python.pluginsource\" library=\"addon.py\">\n    <provides>video</provides>\n  </extension>\n  <extension point=\"xbmc.service\" library=\"service.py\"/>\n  <extension point=\"xbmc.addon.metadata\">\n    <reuselanguageinvoker>true</reuselanguageinvoker>\n    <summary lang=\"cs_CZ\">Netflix</summary>\n    <description lang=\"cs_CZ\">Plugin pro sledování filmů, seriálů online z Netflixu</description>\n    <disclaimer lang=\"cs_CZ\">Použití tohoto doplňku nemusí být ve vaší zemi pobytu legální - před instalací dbejte na vaše zákony.</disclaimer>\n    <summary lang=\"de_DE\">Netflix</summary>","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"addon.xml","time":{"start":1775783762816,"end":1775783762820}}}]}
